4}$N/$^{15}$N and perhaps also low $^{32}$S/$^{34}$S ratios appear to be\ncharacteristic properties of a starburst environment in which massive stars\nhave had sufficient time to affect the isotopic composition of the surrounding\ninterstellar medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 May 2004 12:56:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
