y. We conclude that the hint of\ndiscrepancies in N(HI) distributions most likely arises from small number\nstatistics. Therefore, further observations are required to better clarify the\nimpact of this discrepancy on estimates of Omega_HI at low redshift.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 May 2004 15:21:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
